hannels available on the “Site” for the purpose of operating and promoting the “Application”, in accordance with the privacy policy of the “Application”. \nyour account: \nThe information you provide during the registration process is protected data in accordance with the terms of the privacy policy set out above. You agree to be responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account information, and you also agree to notify Voltum immediately of any unauthorized use of your password or account or any hack In no event will Voltum site be responsible for any loss that you may suffer directly or indirectly, morally or materially, as a result of disclosing your username or password information from any third party. “Usage Agreement” The “Site” administration has the right to suspend or cancel your membership and block you from the “Site.” We also reserve the right to cancel any unconfirmed and unconfirmed accounts, operations or accounts that have been inactive for a long period of time.\nCopyrights: \nThe content, organization, graphics, design, compilation, electronic translation, digitization, and other matters relating to the “Site” are the property of “Al Maady Electrical and Electronic Contracting Company”, and are all subject to the protection provided to it under copyright and trade name laws, and are not These rights include intellectual property rights, and it is absolutely prohibited to copy, redistribute, use or print any of these materials or any part of them from the “Site” or from any other sites, except to the extent permitted by the laws in force in Kuwait in that matter. \nTrademarks: \nThe words and logos on the “website or application” are the property of “Al Maadi Electrical and Electronic Contracting Company” all whether they are registered trademarks, designs, phrases, logos and/or unregistered words and are subject to protection under intellectual property laws. All other trademarks not owned by Voltum that appear on the Site are the property of their respective owners, who may or may not be affiliated with or associated with Voltum.\nTerms of Service Place an order and price details: \nYou can submit a maintenance work service request or a request from one of the stores available through the “website/application” when you register to provide us with the required information. After that, Voltum technicians or our authorized partners will review your request information in accordance with the above privacy policy in the event that you are not provided directly with the price for the requested service. To provide maintenance services at your request, and you can request a technician visit to discover the problem you are facing in the event that you do not know what the required service is. Thus, the price of the service is determined at the customer’s site, knowing that the prices of the maintenance service are variable according to the nature of the labor market. In the event that the offer is accepted, the reservation shall be made and the full amount of the maintenance work service shall be paid upon the provision of the service. The application includes a statement of all maintenance work that you wish to perform. Knowing that in your desire to complete some of the works stipulated in the maintenance work service request when a technician completes the works mentioned in the service request statement; This will not affect the previously agreed fees and you will need to pay the full amount as shown in the service price. And if you want to add some work to the order, it is possible, but the Voltum technician will provide you with the added price for the service, and the Voltum team will update the order invoice to add the added services on the final invoice submitted to you \nadmissions: \nYour agreement to the terms, the contractual relationship between you and Mounjaz arises, and these terms and conditions are superseded by all verbal or written terms and conditions, including the prices display